{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_02_03",
  "title": "小美山愛 3話 ご褒美がほしい",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "みなさーん！　盛り上がってますかー！\nLizNoirは、全開でいきますよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey everyone! Having a good time?\nLizNoir is here for you! Full power!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.233333333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6333.333333333334,
          "startTime": 7.633333333333334
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ライブが始まったばかりなのに会場は凄い熱気だな\n愛も万全のコンディションで調子がよさそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The concert just started but it’s already pumping.\nAi looks like she’s in top condition too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "今日は、このライブに来てくれたみなさんしか\n味わえない、初披露の楽曲もやりまーす！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ve got something special just for you here today!\nThe first chance to hear a brand-new song!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5233.333333333334,
          "startTime": 24.066666666666666
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "実はこの曲のためにずーっと緊張していたんですけど\nこうして莉央さんの背中を借りてたら安心してきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve been so‚ so‚ so nervous about this one‚\nbut Rio has my back! I know it’ll be great!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "もっともっと盛り上げていくから\n最後まで楽しんで下さいねー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re just getting started!\nHold on tight! This is going to be wild!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4500,
          "startTime": 41.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "プレッシャーを感じていたのが嘘みたいに\n伸び伸びとパフォーマンスしているな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All that talk about pressure‚ and she’s killing it on stage.\nWhat a performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "今日のLizNoirはいつも以上に会場を\n沸かせてくれそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "LizNoir always leaves a venue humming\nbut tonight it feels even more intense.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2633.333333333333,
          "startTime": 54.03333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.8
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.8
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！\n私達のステージ、凄かったですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}!\nWe’re doing well‚ aren’t we? It feels incredible out there!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "練習の成果が出ていたな\n新しい振り付けがばっちり決まってたぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All that training paid off.\nEvery single movement was perfect.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.73333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！\nこの調子で後半も頑張ります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you!\nI’ve got plenty left for the second half!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いい笑顔だ\n愛がライブを楽しんでいるのが伝わってくるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can tell from your smile\njust how much you are enjoying this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.36666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "はい！\n前のライブも楽しかったけど今はもっと楽しいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay!\nI always enjoy our concerts‚ but today even more!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.66666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "こないだプレッシャーのお話をしましたよね？\nあの後、みんなともその話をしたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I told you about the pressure I was feeling.\nWell‚ I talked about it with the others as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "私が悩んでいたことを伝えたら、そういう時は\n私達に相談しなさいって莉央さんに言われました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I told them how I was feeling‚\nRio told me to let them know every time I feel that way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.86666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "愛は真面目だからすぐ一人で悩むけど\nもっと仲間を頼っていいのよって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can take things very seriously‚ I know.\nI can bottle them up. She told me not to.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "私のことを大切な仲間だって言ってくれて\n凄く嬉しくなっちゃいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When she told me how much she cares‚\nI got pretty overwhelmed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.76666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……プレッシャーはもう感じていないみたいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sounds like you’re not feeling anymore pressure.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.86666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんなことないです！　プレッシャーはまだ\nありますけど、今はそれも含めて楽しいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-oh no! The pressure is still there‚\nbut I’m now I’m able to enjoy it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "きっと、みんなと一緒だから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s because we’re all together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "今なら……LizNoirのみんなと一緒なら\nどんなプレッシャーにも負ける気がしません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The four of us‚ as one. As LizNoir.\nThat’s why this pressure can’t stop me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、この後も見ていて下さい\n最高のライブにしてみせます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please‚ {user}‚ don’t take your eyes off the stage.\nThis will be the best concert you’ve ever seen!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "四人が嚙み合ったLizNoirは無敵です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The four members of LizNoir are invincible together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブ終了後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After the concert",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.8
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "愛、お疲れ様\n最後まで全力で走りきった最高のライブだったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai. Great job out there.\nYou gave it your all‚ right to the final note!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.86666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai017.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai018.m4a",
      "text": "きっと私一人だけだったら\n今日みたいには歌えませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I’d been out there alone‚\nI never would have been able to sing like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153.33333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai019.m4a",
      "text": "最高のライブが出来たのは、LizNoirのみんなと\n{user}さんが助けてくれたおかげです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This concert was thanks to everyone in LizNoir‚\nand to you‚ {user}‚ for all your help.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai020.m4a",
      "text": "今日のライブでは今までより沢山\nお客さんの笑顔が見られた気がします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It feels like there were more smiling faces\nin the crowd than ever before!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 165.73333333333332
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "それは愛が頑張ったからだよ\n愛がみんなを笑顔にしたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s because you worked so hard‚ Ai.\nYou made all of those smiles happen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai021.m4a",
      "text": "私の歌でみんなが感動してくれて\n笑顔になってくれたのなら凄く嬉しい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m so happy that my singing moved them!\nBringing so much joy makes me happy too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 177.73333333333332
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai022.m4a",
      "text": "……なぜでしょう\nライブは終わったのに、胸の高鳴りが止まりません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t even describe it.\nMy heart is soaring‚ even after the end of the concert.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai023.m4a",
      "text": "私、もっと歌いたい\n早く次のライブがやりたいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to sing some more!\nI can’t wait to sing at the next concert!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 188.86666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それなら俺に任せてくれ。アイドルが\n輝ける舞台を用意するのが仕事だからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Leave that to me. After all‚ it’s my job\nto prepare the stage for you to shine on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai024.m4a",
      "text": "はい、楽しみに待ってます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Great. I’m looking forward to it already!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 198.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、成功したらご褒美がほしいって\n言ってたよな？　結局、何がほしかったんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ you said you wanted a reward\nif the concert were a success. What was it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai025.m4a",
      "text": "それはですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ about that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 206.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 209.13333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai026.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、これからもずっと\n私とLizNoirを見ていて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}‚ I want you to keep on\nwatching over LizNoir!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 212.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 215.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "俺が愛とみんなを見守る……\nそれが愛のしてほしいことなのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Keep on watching over all of you?\nThat’s what you want?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 218.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai027.m4a",
      "text": "きっと私はこれからも一杯悩んだりすると思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sure I’ll have more worries in the future.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 221.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 226.26666666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai028.m4a",
      "text": "そんな時、私達だけじゃ見えない所を\nフォローしてくれる人がいると凄く安心出来るんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Knowing I have people covering my back\nwhen that happens is so reassuring.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 229.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai029.m4a",
      "text": "今回みたいに気にかけてくれるだけで\n安心してステージに立つことが出来るんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s all I need to be able to stand\nup tall up on the stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 235.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 238.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "……分かった\n俺はこれからも愛達を見ているよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Okay.\nI’m happy to do as you ask.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 240.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 244.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai030.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 244.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 246.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai031.m4a",
      "text": "小美山愛はもっともっと成長してみせるので\n見守っていて下さいね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m only going up from here!\nPlease‚ watch me soar!",
